Package comparable

Class Book

java.lang.Object
comparable.Book
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable
public class Book extends Object implements Comparable
The class contains details of the Book id, name, author, and price. Books are sorted by implementing the Comparable interface and duplicates are removed by overriding the hashCode and equals methods from the Object class.
Author:
HATUMA Charles Student at RCA
